此'''伊波拉出血熱暴發列表'''敘述了[[伊波拉出血熱|伊波拉出血熱]]的歷年出現記錄。此病於1976年首次現身，並常在[[撒哈拉以南非洲|非洲撒哈拉以南的地區]]造成間歇性流行。<ref name=SudanEHF/><ref name=ZaireEHF/>目前共有5種[[病毒|病毒]]被[[國際病毒分類委員會|國際病毒分類委員會]]納入[[伊波拉病毒屬|伊波拉病毒屬]]——本迪布焦病毒、雷斯頓病毒、蘇丹病毒、塔伊森林病毒及舊稱“扎伊爾伊波拉病毒”的伊波拉病毒（模式種）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/ICTVdb/Ictv/fs_filov.htm|title=Filoviridae|accessdate=04-10-2009|last1=Netesov|first1=SV|last2=Feldmann|first2=H|last3=Jahrling|first3=PB|last4=Kiley|first4=MP|last5=Klenk|first5=H-D|last6=Sanchez|first6=A|date=2004-04-24|publisher=International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses（[[國際病毒分類委員會|國際病毒分類委員會]]）|archive-date=2010-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100124033425/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/ICTVdb/Ictv/fs_filov.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="PMID19023410">{{cite journal|title=Newly discovered ebola virus associated with hemorrhagic fever outbreak in Uganda|pages=e1000212|issn=1553-7374|journal=PLoS pathogens|volume=4|issue=11|date=2008-11|doi=10.1371/journal.ppat.1000212|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19023410|accessdate=2019-05-25|author=Jonathan S. Towner, Tara K. Sealy, Marina L. Khristova, César G. Albariño, Sean Conlan, Serena A. Reeder, Phenix-Lan Quan, W. Ian Lipkin, Robert Downing, Jordan W. Tappero, Samuel Okware, Julius Lutwama, Barnabas Bakamutumaho, John Kayiwa, James A. Comer, Pierre E. Rollin, Thomas G. Ksiazek, Stuart T. Nichol|pmid=19023410|pmc=PMC2581435|archive-date=2020-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502041936/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19023410|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WHO-PR20080220">{{Cite press release|title=End of Ebola outbreak in Uganda|publisher=World Health Organization（[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]）|date=2008-02-20|url=http://www.who.int/csr/don/2007_02_20b/en/index.html|accessdate=2009-11-29|archive-date=2013-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027040637/http://www.who.int/csr/don/2007_02_20b/en/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中，雷斯頓種只於其他[[靈長動物|靈長動物]]身上誘發疾病。此病甚少直接在{{link-en|天然宿主|Natural Reservoir}}與人類間傳播；每次暴發的[[指示病例|首名患者]]一般是因為觸摸到[[大猩猩|大猩猩]]、[[黑猩猩|黑猩猩]]或[[羚羊|羚羊]]等其他已沾染病毒的野生動物而染病，病毒後透過體液接觸在人類間散播。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Peterson|first1=AT|last2=Bauer|first2=JT|last3=Mills|first3=JN|title=Ecologic and geographic distribution of filovirus disease.|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|date=Jan 2004|volume=10|issue=1|pages=40–7|pmid=15078595|doi=10.3201/eid1001.030125|pmc=3322747|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3322747/|accessdate=2015-02-21|archive-date=2022-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220410220052/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3322747/}}</ref>高危地點通常為[[家庭|家庭]]、[[醫院|醫院]]及[[殮房|殮房]]，因人與人之間的近距離接觸較多。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Questions and Answers about Ebola Hemorrhagic Fever |url=http://www.cdc.gov/ncidod/dvrd/spb/mnpages/dispages/ebola/qa.htm |accessdate=2009-05-31 |date=2009-03-25 |publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090506104535/http://www.cdc.gov/ncidod/dvrd/spb/mnpages/dispages/ebola/qa.htm |archivedate=2009-05-06 }}</ref>在沒有引發較大注意之前，防疫意識較弱之地區的伊波拉患者常被誤診為其他熱帶傳染病（如：[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]、[[傷寒|傷寒]]、[[痢疾|痢疾]]、[[流感|流感]]、各種[[細菌|細菌]]感染等）。總結了過往暴發的經驗，人們制定出更有效的[[公共衛生|公共衛生]]措施，設立於高危地區的[[世衛組織|世衛組織]]全球疫症與應對網絡為其中一例。非洲亦設立了在地實驗室以便更有效地確診疑似個案，並無需像過往般通過航海取得海外實驗室的樣本及鑑定結果。<ref name="10.1371/journal.pmed.0010059">{{cite journal|title=Containing the Threat—Don't Forget Ebola|doi=10.1371/journal.pmed.0010059|url=http://journals.plos.org/plosmedicine/article?id=10.1371/journal.pmed.0010059|date=2004-12-28|journal=PLOS Medicine|volume=1|issue=3|pages=e59|issn=1549-1676|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Jonathan Cohen|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927070518/https://journals.plos.org/plosmedicine/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pmed.0010059|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[美國疾病控制與預防中心|美國疾病控制與預防中心]]（特殊病原體關注組）有密切留意疾病流行的情況。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cdc.gov/ncidod/dvrd/spb/mnpages/whoweare.htm |title=Mission Statement |date=2007-10-31 |publisher=National Center for Infectious Diseases & Centers for Disease Control and Prevention |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091113002157/http://www.cdc.gov/ncidod/dvrd/Spb/mnpages/whoweare.htm |archivedate=2009-11-13 |accessdate=2015-02-11 }}</ref>

